---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Who am I?">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-prose">
    <div class="prose-h2:my-0">
      <h2 class="font-thin lowercase italic line-through">
        Yasin is an extravagant, extraordinary, extraterrestrial fullstack and
        big stack and tiny stack developer and designer and COO and CTO and CEO.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 prose-h2:my-0 prose-img:my-0">
      <h2>Hi, I am Yasin and I live in Lower Austria.</h2>
      <img
        class="size-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-white shadow"
        src="/map.png"
        alt="Map showing europe and Lower Austria"
      />
    </div>
    <p>
      I have worked as a backend, frontend and fullstack developer for many
      years. I also have experience in hardware, networking and almost every
      product line from Microsoft that is used in enterprises.
    </p>
    <p>
      I had the chance to work with the following technologies/frameworks and
      write code in these languages to date:
    </p>
    <p class="font-medium">
      React, Next.js, TypeScript, JavaScript, .NET (C#), Blazor, Laravel (PHP),
      Vue.js, Docker, Kubernetes, Swift, PowerShell, React Native, Expo and
      Bash.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
